    "The uniqueness of each feature is further enhanced by the unsupervised geometric consistency loss function.",
    "The model uses two normal forms to predict the rigid transformation: unsupervised geometric consistency loss, which is used to minimize the geometric distance between the transformation source and the target point cloud; By having a supervised transformation loss, which is used to estimate the rigid motion itself.",
